            "title": "盤中速報 - 高知特科技(CTSH-US)大漲5%，報75.97美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高知特科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CTSH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CTSH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CTSH-US</a>)截至台北時間22日00:57股價上漲3.62美元，報75.97美元，漲幅5%，成交量3,005,501（股），盤中最高價75.97美元、最低價72.66美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+1.34%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+1.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.96%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.72%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>高知特科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CTSH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CTSH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CTSH-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.73%</li> <li>近 1 月：+8.38%</li> <li>近 3 月：+2.55%</li> <li>近 6 月：-10.74%</li> <li>今年以來：-5.39%</li></ul></section></main>",
